Package: quizR
Type: Package
Title: Create moodle quizzes with and for R
Version: 1.0
Date: 2016-09-24
Author: Sylvain Rousseau
Maintainer: Sylvain Rousseau <sylvain.rousseau@hds.utc.fr>
Description: The main feature of this package is to be able to create XML files designed to be imported as quizzes in the LMS Moodle. There are additional features for R quizzes like automatic grades based on the CSV file of results provided by Moodle, PDF file of quizzes, R file of datasets used in the quiz.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Imports:
    pryr,
    rmarkdown,
    digest,
    stringr,
    stringi,
    utils,
    tools,
    logging
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Suggests: testthat
